  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To prospectively collect ascites, pleural fluid, circulating tumor cells and derived primary
      cultures from metastatic cancer patients. The specimens will be analyzed using
      DNA/RNA/proteomic approaches.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
